snippet.title: Coreborn | Story Trailer
snippet.description:
🎮WISHLIST NOW on Steam: https://bit.ly/WishlistCoreborn
💬Join Coreborn Discord for updates and playtests: https://discord.gg/coreborn

Coreborn, initially coming to Early Access on PC, will be a free-to-play, cross-platform social survival sandbox game. It is being built on three main gameplay pillars: Survival sandbox (the world of Tormentosia), Adventures (diverse action experiences), and Social hub (Coreheim, the location of the Ultracore).

Follow Coreborn
Twitter | Instagram | TikTok: @playCoreborn
